                <note rend="inline" type="source">882.20/481: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Bullitt</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1939-08-05T13:00:00-04:00"
                            >August 5, 1939—1 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>590. Your 1446, August 4, 7 p.m.<note n="45" xml:id="d677fn45">Not
                        printed.</note> The President yesterday approved a solution different from
                    that which he had previously had under consideration. I am sending you the full
                    text by mail.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
